Hey Spin family, we updated our app. Check out what's new and improved!

What’s new:
- We’re introducing a brand new feature where riders get the first 30 minutes free if you ride selected bikes to a designated zone!

Bug fixes:
- We updated ride cost totals to reflect the amount of credits spent on each trip.
- We’re allowing riders to reset their password!

Hey Spin family, we updated our app. Check out what's new and improved!

What’s new:
- We’re introducing a brand new feature where riders get the first 30 minutes free if you ride selected bikes to a designated zone!

Bug fixes:
- We updated ride cost totals to reflect the amount of credits spent on each trip.
- We’re allowing riders to reset their password!
